Package: memory-monitor
Version: 1.0.1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), curl, procps, bc
Maintainer: System Administrator khusniddin989@gmail.com
Description: System Resource Monitoring Tool
 A comprehensive system monitoring tool that tracks RAM, CPU, 
 and disk usage and sends alerts via Telegram when thresholds 
 are exceeded. Features include configurable thresholds, 
 detailed logging, and information about top resource-consuming 
 processes.
